g.text: Devops is a culture that aims to improve your
organization's Ability to Deliver the applications.
Suppose you have your application already delivered
but now you want to add a new feature to your app,
now everything is ready including coding part but still
to deliver your app it is taking 10 days time. This is
not a good way at the enterprice level.
- So to automate and deliver the applications faster
we need proper devops done in the organization.
- But just delivering application doesn't mean devops
delivering application with Quality, Automations, testing
Devops is a process of improving the delivery of applications
To understand the need of Devops lets go back into the time when thier

To complete all the above process it may take 10 days of time

So the delivery time is reduced resulting in faster application
delivery. Devops, is need in the organization.
